1 A BILL for an Act to provide an appropriation for defraying the expenses of the veterans' home;
2 to create and enact a new section to chapter 37-15 of the North Dakota Century Code, relating
3 to meals provided to employees of the veterans' home; to provide an exemption; to provide for a
4 legislative management study; and to declare an emergency.
